'''Lovinobaňa''' is a village and municipality in the [[Lučenec District]] in the [[Banská Bystrica Region]] of [[Slovakia]].
==History==
In [[history|historical record]]s the village was first mentioned in 1336.
==Geography==
The municipality lies at an altitude of 255 metres and covers and area of 21.130km². It has a population of about 2100 people.
